### Ascend API — Analytics
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT

### Get dashboard snapshot (cached, refreshed every 5 min)
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Daily analytics (last 30 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/daily?days=30
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Weekly analytics (last 12 weeks)
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/weekly?weeks=12
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Monthly analytics (last 12 months)
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/monthly?months=12
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Force refresh dashboard snapshot
POST {{baseUrl}}/analytics/snapshot/refresh
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
